snippet.textDisplay: Admit it or not, Lost Stories saved this song with their great music. Anuv Jain did sing it well, but his voice isn’t something extraordinary or something you can keep on repeat. I’m not someone who compares our music with Pakistani music, but we should at least understand that this isn’t the best level of music. The lyrics also feel too cluttered.
snippet.textOriginal: Admit it or not, Lost Stories saved this song with their great music. Anuv Jain did sing it well, but his voice isn’t something extraordinary or something you can keep on repeat. I’m not someone who compares our music with Pakistani music, but we should at least understand that this isn’t the best level of music. The lyrics also feel too cluttered.
